      • Serialization Methods

        • readResolve

          private java.lang.Object readResolve()
          This method makes the Singleton Pattern play nicely with deserialization in our application. Since deserialization creates a new object, we clear the old instance, and add all the Products from the deserialized object (this) to the instance, then return the instance, rather than this.
